{"tid":267861,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無啲書睇完心智會成熟一啲 年紀大過我既唔肯同我做朋友","createTime":"2017-06-02T14:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T11:16:48.000Z","uid":27793,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"230fca586d998d732b87c9bbc7a59ea8f41b4c43","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"我22歲人 啱啱grad<br />\n講野越來越低能<br />\n被屋企人話我無黎氣質<br />\n雖然可以個樣扮有氣質<br />\n但一相處落都「露晒底」咁<br />\n<br />\n公司年紀大翻少少既都唔肯同我做朋友<br />\n我諗係時候要改善下<br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地鬧我啊 <br />\n或者任何有咩書/作家推介比我都會萬分感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1723e71738173384c767767712af78329fbdf5a6","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"59770d55aa142ea07c70d936638b5c8fd66522bf","tid":267861,"uid":28669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"社會經驗要慢慢學<br />\n急唔黎"},{"pid":"d723ad8faeabeb77471b8c0f2d562370017da582","tid":267861,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"改下秒推先"},{"pid":"9e260114f74d517af72ccb049c42be5282dac9f9","tid":267861,"uid":63765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"認真 得閒睇下勵志書<br />\n因為成熟唔可以一時間改變 可能有啲大事件發生咗係你身上令到你對某件事既價值觀改變咗先至有機會比你成熟<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下從基本日常生活試下改變先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f05c159905fc83c3c3ce4fe0581c90a06859f","tid":267861,"uid":79471,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真 得閒睇下勵志書<br />\n因為成熟唔可以一時間改變 可能有啲大事件發生咗係你身上令到你對某件事既價值觀改變咗先至有機會比你成熟<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下從基本日常生活試下改變先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好睇勵志書<br />\n只會黑人憎"},{"pid":"5abd9e54cb7c3101e61e8129b4641e7bc52e5cca","tid":267861,"uid":93114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"返下勞動階層嘅工<br />\n個人會自理能力高啲 EQ高啲 仲有好多師傅全部都係人生經驗資料館"},{"pid":"e17884769d2f07d34144f5983e2a640b426603e8","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190b0bfa5449c2b76b5d21bb6ebdf935fe01311b","tid":267861,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪想返？"},{"pid":"c5356e776236e7b31cbc98f84ff37259d3e0714f","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返下勞動階層嘅工<br />\n個人會自理能力高啲 EQ高啲 仲有好多師傅全部都係人生經驗資料館</blockquote><br />\n我老豆係地盤判頭 我可以隨時返<br />\n雖然我係一個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵日有機會我去體驗！<br />\n一定會"},{"pid":"f03316a7b5f891aaba1992ade4f0b57e015d74c0","tid":267861,"uid":39402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真 得閒睇下勵志書<br />\n因為成熟唔可以一時間改變 可能有啲大事件發生咗係你身上令到你對某件事既價值觀改變咗先至有機會比你成熟<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下從基本日常生活試下改變先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好睇勵志書<br />\n只會<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人憎</span></blockquote><br />\n何以見得?<br />\n<br />\nBTW 答番樓主<br />\n好難定義人心智成唔成熟<br />\n我諗唔好講埋d低能野 正經小小會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"12a1208384ebb3e639d025236928ec032401d56e","tid":267861,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"心智成熟點會諗住同公司同事做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8948065a42036f451d3e200e10b35c638fcf35","tid":267861,"uid":79471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真 得閒睇下勵志書<br />\n因為成熟唔可以一時間改變 可能有啲大事件發生咗係你身上令到你對某件事既價值觀改變咗先至有機會比你成熟<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下從基本日常生活試下改變先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好睇勵志書<br />\n只會<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人憎</span></blockquote><br />\n何以見得?<br />\n<br />\nBTW 答番樓主<br />\n好難定義人心智成唔成熟<br />\n我諗唔好講埋d低能野 正經小小會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n人成長靠經歷 睇其他人經歷唔會係勵志書啦<br />\n嗰啲叫傳記 好多都唔勵志嘅<br />\n勵志書強行灌輸觀念<br />\n你把口講返出嚟好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出嚟做嘢見唔少"},{"pid":"fd04e46340776134d340295b5b23b1a9c604b87a","tid":267861,"uid":1525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真 得閒睇下勵志書<br />\n因為成熟唔可以一時間改變 可能有啲大事件發生咗係你身上令到你對某件事既價值觀改變咗先至有機會比你成熟<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下從基本日常生活試下改變先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好睇勵志書<br />\n只會<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人憎</span></blockquote><br />\n何以見得?<br />\n<br />\nBTW 答番樓主<br />\n好難定義人心智成唔成熟<br />\n我諗唔好講埋d低能野 正經小小會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n人成長靠經歷 睇其他人經歷唔會係勵志書啦<br />\n嗰啲叫傳記 好多都唔勵志嘅<br />\n勵志書強行灌輸觀念<br />\n你把口講返出嚟好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出嚟做嘢見唔少</blockquote><br />\n我都唔推勵志書 <br />\n唔知點解覺得好洗腦 好有邪教feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c9dbe3e470ec4f8202d2ae695d7e3405d5ac9f","tid":267861,"uid":93114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返下勞動階層嘅工<br />\n個人會自理能力高啲 EQ高啲 仲有好多師傅全部都係人生經驗資料館</blockquote><br />\n我老豆係地盤判頭 我可以隨時返<br />\n雖然我係一個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵日有機會我去體驗！<br />\n一定會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你一定明白啦 地盤未必係最高尚嘅地方<br />\n不過地盤嗰種環境就係會造就到最起碼要自己顧掂自己 同時間出入地盤一班兄弟都會守望相助<br />\n<br />\n地盤佬又吋 又夠直接 你係錯就會屌你 <br />\n唔醒目又會屌你 <br />\n<br />\n師傅經驗嘅又比自己多 其實你肯學佢地都好願意教<br />\n地盤真係個好地方"},{"pid":"c426b30003d6319628e57bbb17cd360228d93366","tid":267861,"uid":21249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪少少事都唔識自理 甚至乎會慣性求助於人果d人黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ade1fef8189bdc4a670543231770c7070e33eb","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心智成熟點會諗住同公司同事做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢哋識好多野<br />\n舉止行為好優雅得體<br />\n<br />\n見到優秀嘅人我就想去認識佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都唔係大我好多姐 想做個朋友佢哋都唔肯<br />\n26-7 我22咋嘛"},{"pid":"8a9e78b2a3113cae6c4c05600aed18e6928a23a7","tid":267861,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪少少事都唔識自理 甚至乎會慣性求助於人果d人黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a01adf92c6561ff6cff8b6066ff3a793ce270b","tid":267861,"uid":9053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"米蘭昆德拉"},{"pid":"c57754d526758df063736ebc14e9a7a6b7a383d1","tid":267861,"uid":43141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T